      "description": "The Eventbrite app is the place to get into… whatever you're into. From shows to hobbies,from the club to that new craze—Eventbrite is your place to discover, book, and share all the experiences you’re excited about out there. \n\nFIND IT: Discover more new things to do. \n  \nOur Discover tab is your personalized feed, with more recommendations, search, and filtering options to inspire your next adventure.\nWe’re introducing It-Lists*: Insider guides to cool and unexpected happenings in your city, curated by some of our favorite people and brands. *Initially available in select cities.\n  \nBOOK IT: Commit with confidence.\n\nWe’ve added good-to-know info to our listings.\nYou can now vibe check before checkout with better photos and videos of locations and events.\n\nSHARE IT: And see what everyone’s got going on.\n\nFollow friends and share events you’re excited about.\nSee who’s going and find out first when friends book tickets, so you can too.\nEasily import contacts, find friends, choose organizers to follow, and manage your followers all in the Account tab.\n\nGET INTO IT: It’s everything you need, right in one place. \n\nNever lose track of your best-laid plans with our new like and save features.\nEasily find your tickets in the dedicated tab, or save them to your phone wallet.\nQuick access to last minute key event information such as location and time so that you’re always prepared.\n\nWhat’s Eventbrite?\n\nEventbrite enables anyone to create, promote, and sell tickets to any event imaginable, while also helping people discover and share events that match their passions. Whether it’s a neighborhood block party, an exciting new artist, or that show you’ve had on your calendar for months, Eventbrite helps you get into it.\n\nINFORMATION SHARING: When purchasing tickets or registering for an event, we provide the information entered to the event organizer so they can manage the event. Please review our Privacy Policy and California Privacy Notice for more information on your choices around information sharing.\n\nCalifornia Privacy Notice: \nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/support/articles/en_US/Troubleshooting/supplemental-privacy-notice-for-california-residents?lg=en_US",
